paragraph: The acquisition date fair value of net assets acquired during fiscal year 2020 was $612 million, consisting of $679 million of assets acquired and $67 million of liabilities assumed. The goodwill is not deductible for tax purposes. The Company recognized $80 million of contingent consideration liabilities in connection with business combinations during fiscal year 2020, which are comprised of revenue and regulatory milestone based payments. Purchase price allocation adjustments for fiscal year 2020 business combinations were not significant.
